    {\displaystyle P(x)=a_{0}x^{n}+a_{i}x^{n-1}+\cdots +a_{n},}
   its homogenization is the bivariate polynomial 
  
    
      
        
          
            P
            ¯
          
        
        (
        x
        ,
        y
        )
        =
        
          a
          
